        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉一詮Q1獲利暴增36倍 散熱轉型效益顯現周漲逾兩成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">LED 導線架暨均熱片一詮 (2486-TW) 受惠於人工智慧應用帶動高階散熱需求噴發，稅後純益錄得 0.71 億元，且較去年同期大幅增長 36 倍，單季每股純益為 0.31 元，24 日終場收在 224 元，創波段高點，周漲幅超過 21 ％，周成交量 2164 張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一詮目前憑藉人工智慧與光通訊散熱雙線並進，訂單能見度已上看至 2027 年。目前產品已成功打入輝達與谷歌供應鏈，成為市場上極少數能穩定供應高階先進封裝散熱片的業者之一，三月營收亦在相關高階應用帶動下繳出年增近兩成的佳績。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d114c3dd-5c82-368d-88cd-e3d330d76192-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為了支應北美雲端龍頭與客製化晶片客戶的強勁需求，一詮 (2486-TW) 計畫在 2026 年將整體產能較去年大幅提升一倍。公司已積極進行設備與廠房投資，並將傳統 LED 產線移往中國大陸江門廠區，藉此將國內產能全面改裝為均熱片與補強片專線以應對高毛利專案。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"一詮日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q_2pJqBE.pLFn0zFrs3Nrg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/f83207618a8